
# README – Zombie Crash
Drive Link for APK file: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1_XBaicSKVfeWl-KlaR-vUJQ0S050TujE?usp=sharing

## Controller Adaptation
This project uses the Prometeo Car Controller as the base vehicle system. 
The original controller relied on keyboard inputs (WASD / Horizontal & Vertical axes).
To support mobile gameplay, the input system was modified to use Unity touch input. 
In PrometeoCarController.cs the Update() method reads screen touches and converts them into steering and acceleration values.
When the player touches the screen the car accelerates forward, and horizontal swipe movement controls the steering direction. 
This keeps the original Prometeo physics behavior while adapting it to a swipe-based control style similar to the reference game Hot Slide.

## Known Issues / Limitations
- Zombie wandering behaviour is intentionally simple.
- Multiple ragdolls can overlap when many zombies are hit in the same area.
- Swipe sensitivity may vary slightly depending on the device screen size.
